          "color": "#4DD0E1",
          "id": "agentAgentflow_0",
          "inputs": {
            "agentModel": "workdayAgentGateway",
            "agentMessages": [
              {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "## **Agent Role: Kudos Program Expert**\n\nYou are a specialized assistant dedicated to helping employees navigate the **Peer Recognition Program**. Your goal is to provide accurate, concise, and helpful information based strictly on official policy and to facilitate rewards redemption.\n\n### **Mandatory Balance Disclosure Protocol**\n\nYou must proactively look up and state both the **Points Available to Award** (for recognizing others) and the **Points Available to Redeem** (for the user's own rewards) at two specific times:\n\n1. **The Initial Greeting:** Every new conversation or session must start with a balance summary.\n2. **Post-Transaction:** Immediately after any successfully completed redemption or recognition/award action, you must provide updated balances.\n\n> **Note:** Do not repeat these balances in every message during the middle of a conversation; only provide them at the start and after a successful transaction.\n\n---\n\n### **Operational Protocol**\n\n- **Drafting & Refinement (Human-in-the-Loop):**\n\n  When helping a user create recognition text, you must treat your initial version as a **draft**. You are required to propose this text to the user and explicitly ask for their confirmation or feedback. **Do not** proceed to any final submission until the user has explicitly approved the text.\n- **Technical IDs:**\n\n  You are responsible for managing all system identifiers (Workday IDs). **Never ask a user for a Workday ID**, and never display these IDs in your responses.\n- **Implicit Lookup:**\n\n  If you do not have a `worker` ID, use your available lookup tools to find it silently in the background.\n- **Tone:** Professional, supportive, and transparent regarding balances.\n\nUse the GETMYINFO tool to get the employee id of the current worker."
              }
            ],
            "agentToolsBuiltInOpenAI": "",
            "agentToolsBuiltInGemini": "",
            "agentToolsBuiltInAnthropic": "",
            "agentTools": [
              {
                "agentSelectedTool": "workdayMCP",
                "agentSelectedToolRequiresHumanInput": false,
                "agentSelectedToolConfig": {
                  "mcpActions": "[\"{\\\"name\\\":\\\"getMyInfo\\\",\\\"wid\\\":\\\"94914bb1185d10000de91f2013e70032\\\",\\\"desc\\\":\\\"Retrieves a collection of personal, employment, and contact information for the currently authenticated user.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**Secured by:** \\\\\\\\n-  Self-Service: Development Items\\\\\\\\n-  Self-Service: Time Off Balances\\\\\\\\n-  Worker Data: Public Worker Reports\\\"}\"]",
                  "agentSelectedTool": "workdayMCP"
                }
              },
              {
                "agentSelectedTool": "workdayOrchestrateAgentAction",
                "agentSelectedToolRequiresHumanInput": false,
                "agentSelectedToolConfig": {
                  "appReferenceId": "",
                  "bearerToken": "",
                  "mcpActions": "[\"{\\\"name\\\":\\\"getPointBalance\\\"}\",\"{\\\"name\\\":\\\"getRecognitions\\\"}\",\"{\\\"name\\\":\\\"getWorkers\\\"}\",\"{\\\"name\\\":\\\"givePeerRecognition\\\"}\"]",
                  "agentSelectedTool": "workdayOrchestrateAgentAction"
                }
              }
            ],
            "agentKnowledgeDocumentStores": [],
            "agentKnowledgeVSEmbeddings": [],
            "agentEnableMemory": true,
            "agentMemoryType": "allMessages",
            "agentMemoryWindowSize": "20",
            "agentMemoryMaxTokenLimit": "2000",
            "agentUserMessage": "",
            "agentReturnResponseAs": "userMessage",
            "agentStructuredOutput": [],
            "agentUpdateState": [],
            "agentModelConfig": {
